content.rendered:
Directed By Kosaraju Harikrishna

Written By Vasudev Muneppagari. Mallidi Vasishta

Stars Rajeev Kanakala (Rajiv). Vennela Kishore. Samyuktha Menon (Vyjayanthi). Vinni Mobstaz (Villain side role). Nandamuri Kalyan Ram (Bimbisara). Srinivasa Reddy. Sathviksriram (Guest Apperance). Catherine Tresa (Aira)

Language Hindi

Producers Kosaraju Harikrishna

Production NTR Arts
